Notes: SP led from start to finish and still has not trailed in any of its five games
this season...SP led 28-21 in second half and went on 8-0 run for 15-point
lead...Leading 43-29 with 11 minutes left, SP went on 18-2 run over next six
minutes for 61-31 lead...SP ranked fourth in latest D3hoops.com national poll.
Game.Officials: Tom Kissinger,  Donna Wegner,  Jack Blume
